<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>3978</hymn_number>
<author>Christian Sferra</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 You are my friend
 I trust in You
 Never abandon me
 Always be true
 You are my world
 I live in You
 Though many things are around
 I look to You
 You are my everything
 Cannot live without You
 You are the air I breath

[V2]
 And I'll never know
 Where I would be
 If I didn't have You
 Don't know if I could make it through
 Without Your hand holding me
 You are my Jesus
 You are my Jesus</lyrics>
<title>You are my friend</title>
</song>